

"""
Global Stock Data Extractor — Multi-Country, 50-Year Daily Data
================================================================
Improvements over baseline:
  - Central exchange suffix registry (no per-country hardcoding)
  - Persistent ticker cache (JSON) — survives re-runs
  - Batch market-cap fetching (fast, not one-by-one)
  - Retry + backoff for yfinance throttling
  - Parallel country downloads via ThreadPoolExecutor
  - Robust Wikipedia scraping with multiple column name fallbacks
  - Market-cap ranking done efficiently
"""

